title:Broccoli Cheddar Soup
ingredients:1/4 cup chopped onion//
1/4 cup butter, cubed//
1/4 cup all-purpose flour//
1/4 teaspoon salt//
1/4 teaspoon pepper//
1-1/2 cups milk//
3/4 cup chicken broth//
1 cup cooked chopped broccoli//
1/2 cup shredded cheddar cheese
instructions:In a small saucepan, saute onion in butter until tender.//
Stir in the flour, salt and pepper until blended; gradually add milk and broth.//
Bring to a boil.//
Cook and stir until thickened, about 2 minutes.//
Add broccoli.//
Cook and stir until heated through.//
Remove from the heat, stir in cheese until melted.